Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.80,0:00:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.90,0:00:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.40,0:00:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是克勞士嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.03,0:00:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.74,0:00:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我聽得到你的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.71,0:00:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士你現在在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.98,0:00:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒呢？艾兒沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.51,0:00:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒也和我在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.21,0:00:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.48,0:00:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就相信你一定還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.32,0:00:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.22,0:00:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.06,0:00:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們都沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.69,0:00:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒和我都沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.60,0:00:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是亞力克斯他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.67,0:00:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯還留在基爾特城裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.21,0:00:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，你能到龍之牙來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.95,0:00:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有靠艾兒薇絲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.38,0:00:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要把EXILE...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.56,0:01:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞，蘇菲亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.93,0:01:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞，發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.29,0:01:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.10,0:01:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞，蘇菲亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.40,0:01:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.44,0:01:25.84,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.91,0:01:29.44,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.52,0:01:36.65,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說把黎明　當作是一個開始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.72,0:01:43.76,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說現在就是來臨的時刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.83,0:01:48.33,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,與你的煙雲時代交響曲 飛向雲海的彼端 \N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony  雲の海の向こうに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.40,0:01:58.14,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飛往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.38,0:02:12.62,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那瞬間？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.69,0:02:27.10,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜  我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに  二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.17,0:02:37.11,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.45,0:03:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸，媽...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.19,0:03:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.86,0:03:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}安靜的一步\NQuiet move
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.03,0:03:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是基爾特控制住了EXILE嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.50,0:04:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.70,0:04:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮總帥她應該不知道\N全部的關鍵謎詩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.60,0:04:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體船艦回到我這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.31,0:04:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特開始撤退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.54,0:04:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.09,0:04:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離基爾特艦隊還有500呎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.80,0:05:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.58,0:05:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前鋒艦隊發生連串船身爆炸聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經超過聽音極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.82,0:05:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止追擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體艦隊後退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.63,0:05:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去保護麥德賽司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.36,0:05:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖猶士坦號\N轉到克勞索拉斯號的右舷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.54,0:05:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六號艦它...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.95,0:06:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖猶士坦號遭到擊沈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.34,0:06:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那道光是...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.42,0:06:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼EXILE不會去攻擊\N戴芬妮總帥坐的船艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.26,0:06:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE，你真是太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.03,0:06:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我對你是特別的對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.63,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.34,0:06:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是不需要四個關鍵謎詩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1，2...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.83,0:07:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下一個標識處\N轉向1點鐘方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.43,0:07:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後直直走就到龍之牙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.60,0:07:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.94,0:07:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳越來越曉得怎麼領航了呢\N艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都要感謝拉薇的筆記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.91,0:07:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.64,0:07:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇她也常常像這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.35,0:07:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一邊看著筆記一邊飛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.72,0:07:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒和我都沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是亞力克斯他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.79,0:07:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯還留在基爾特城裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.33,0:07:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，你能到龍之牙來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.43,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有靠艾兒薇絲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.46,0:07:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要把EXILE...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.40,0:07:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如您所見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.23,0:07:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地上的人也開始可以\N自由通信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.97,0:08:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你通知我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.84,0:08:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有件事要麻煩你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.38,0:08:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望EXILE\N就保持現在這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.98,0:08:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不需要艾兒薇絲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.73,0:08:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了，艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.49,0:08:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是龍之牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.70,0:08:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好壯觀，真的就像是龍的牙齒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒艇接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備信號彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.92,0:08:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們正在準備讓我們進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.52,0:08:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃料還夠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心，艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.26,0:08:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是足夠撐到那裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要加速了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.54,0:09:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩幫我們補給...咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.61,0:09:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊薩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.48,0:09:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，果然跟我想的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.89,0:09:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破得不成樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.02,0:09:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.12,0:09:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.82,0:09:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要說的不是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.26,0:09:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們去轉搭那架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.06,0:09:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗絲...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你放心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.10,0:09:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦的大夥都平安無事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.07,0:09:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你打算駕著這架\N快要報廢的先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.37,0:09:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挑戰大風暴區嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.44,0:09:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你光是飛到這裡都很吃力了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光用看的也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.02,0:09:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以在這裡我們幫你準備了\N全新的機體和領航員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是副艦長的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.79,0:09:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞的命令？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.96,0:09:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.09,0:10:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和艾兒要繼續搭先鋒艇\N前往銀之戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.63,0:10:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.68,0:10:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞地亞壓，沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.11,0:10:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認燃料，全滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.82,0:10:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒，妳可以不用這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.49,0:10:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不用再導航了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，辛苦妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.59,0:10:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家好不容易才學會的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.40,0:10:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我看還是麻煩妳好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.44,0:10:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，伊薩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.51,0:10:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.76,0:11:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好運，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到電波脈衝音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.47,0:11:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發信源在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.34,0:12:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了，是度西斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.31,0:12:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.38,0:12:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE開始移動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它正在後退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.82,0:12:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去追EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.65,0:12:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持距離前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.53,0:12:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從度西斯是吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.03,0:12:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時候終於到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.80,0:12:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新世界的大門就要打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前方有亂流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.48,0:12:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方位，朝右修正3度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.15,0:12:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解，朝右修正3度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.49,0:12:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正牌的領航員果然不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.39,0:12:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現第二中繼地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗絲，發射信號彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.30,0:12:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.01,0:13:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了喔，在七點鐘方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.55,0:13:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了，一號機正在等你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.19,0:13:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.46,0:13:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個大姊姊要擔任領航嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.72,0:13:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.93,0:13:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她今天也在生氣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.10,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，她沒有在生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.43,0:13:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也並不是老在生氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.43,0:13:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.00,0:13:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是太認真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.31,0:13:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實她人很好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.44,0:13:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點我最清楚不過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士他也這麼說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.12,0:13:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.45,0:13:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始\N妳也可以跟她做朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.22,0:13:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜她的領航經驗\N不是很豐富
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.66,0:13:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以艾兒妳要幫她哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.43,0:13:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:13:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇在你的先鋒艇那裡等著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.83,0:14:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.77,0:14:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.31,0:14:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們，艾麗絲，寇斯塔比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.04,0:14:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.68,0:14:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當心點哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.29,0:14:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.46,0:14:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾經說過你想知道\N這片天空裡發生了什麼對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.30,0:14:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在就飛在\N你想瞭解的這片天空正中央
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.81,0:14:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和艾兒被基爾特囚禁的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.25,0:14:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒能保護艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒能救出亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.15,0:14:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有迪奧和魯修拉也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.49,0:14:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這片天空裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.26,0:15:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能當個...旁觀者而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.63,0:15:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有東西接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.11,0:15:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，是基爾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們正上方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.92,0:15:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們發現艾兒在這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.25,0:15:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，保護艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.86,0:15:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.27,0:15:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.33,0:15:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE不是需要艾兒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你難道沒有感覺\N星型機的彈道帶著殺氣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.97,0:15:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兩架是當真打算擊落我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.54,0:15:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,備用彈匣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.68,0:15:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.81,0:15:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子彈只剩200發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.38,0:15:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.64,0:16:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把備用燃料箱丟掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.01,0:16:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機身太重了不好操縱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.38,0:16:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.05,0:16:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會沒辦法撐到下個補給點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.96,0:16:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，看妳一臉鬱卒的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛溫...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞌睡蟲他們好慢哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.83,0:16:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是要比預定的時間慢些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要擺出這種表情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有隊長跟著他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.64,0:17:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從飛行船飛到這裡\N一下就到了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到一號機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.38,0:17:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離15000，一點鐘方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在和星型機交戰中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.83,0:17:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.90,0:17:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有到下個補給點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.50,0:17:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，如果是這個距離的話\N應該有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.47,0:17:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當下給他們點顏色瞧瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把備用燃料箱丟下去了\N你瞄準它射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子彈剩下多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.07,0:17:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不到30發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.14,0:17:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.51,0:17:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中斷動力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.34,0:18:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星型機被擊落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.69,0:18:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你並不只是個旁觀者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.93,0:18:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你成功保護了艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.32,0:18:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.92,0:18:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.56,0:18:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.40,0:19:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.61,0:19:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.44,0:19:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好妳沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.22,0:19:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才的表現還真精彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.29,0:19:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛溫，蓋爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.15,0:19:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你越來越厲害囉，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.72,0:19:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的真命天女在等你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.23,0:19:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了別嚇到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.63,0:19:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它可是為了大風暴區\N特別作了調整哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，我們說好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.66,0:20:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起飛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.57,0:20:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,節流閥確認關閉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.41,0:20:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基礎檢查，完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發動引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.22,0:20:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.49,0:20:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長交給你的那首重要的詩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.26,0:20:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒忘記吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.59,0:20:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.86,0:20:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，請打開裝甲閘門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.21,0:20:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們，葛溫，蓋爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.95,0:20:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.22,0:20:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.34,0:21:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你幸運，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.00,0:21:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願順風與你同在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大氣速度90節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大氣速度95節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.13,0:21:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以把頭抬起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.17,0:21:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大氣速度100節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.14,0:21:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.38,0:21:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊，艾兒也沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.51,0:22:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大氣速度150節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.12,0:22:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，要注意雨候鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.48,0:22:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭...\N瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.52,0:22:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色的...先鋒艇！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.26,0:22:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，一整天沒見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.85,0:22:40.15,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的時光逐漸逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.75,0:22:46.78,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你離我如此接近感覺  卻好遠…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.86,0:22:52.06,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什麼\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.13,0:22:57.80,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.87,0:23:03.61,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你奮不顧身的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.68,0:23:12.38,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種透明的美麗  令我噤聲無語\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.45,0:23:18.22,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飛往天際\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.29,0:23:24.13,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我願成為你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.20,0:23:29.93,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,無論風有多麼強\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.00,0:23:35.74,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永遠不會折斷的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.81,0:23:45.95,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我會擁有那樣一對翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.42,0:23:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（下回預告）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.26,0:23:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭是消耗戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.96,0:23:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使流再多的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.70,0:23:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也要趁現在讓世界\N從基爾特的統治下獲得解放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.53,0:24:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甩開觸手殺出一條血路來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.27,0:24:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大夥拼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.54,0:24:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備魚雷，定時信管12...\N不，5秒就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.74,0:24:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體砲門發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.24,0:24:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最後流亡 第26話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.15,0:24:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棄子\NResign
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.31,0:24:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏爾班號撞壞\N不要停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.18,0:24:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算用拖的也要前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.32,0:24:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漸減口徑式重高角砲，發射
